title: Martin big winner at Capital Football Referee Award Night (ACT Football Federation Inc)
text: ( Source : ACT Football Federation Inc) Gavin Martin was awarded the coveted Nicholas Szego Trophy at the Capital Football Referees presentation night. The Nicholas Szego Trophy is the award for referees' referee of the year and is voted on
